pretty much

00:07:30.601 --> 00:07:33.100
just build it once
and use it everywhere.

00:07:33.100 --> 00:07:35.667
Deploy it to multiple
social networks.

00:07:35.667 --> 00:07:37.767
We have some
great applications

00:07:37.767 --> 00:07:41.534
that are running
on two-dozen social networks.

00:07:41.534 --> 00:07:45.167
And we also have--
