Google App Engine

00:07:47.567 --> 00:07:49.767
that allows you
to scale the back end

00:07:49.767 --> 00:07:52.767
from one server
to potentially 1,000 servers

00:07:52.767 --> 00:07:54.801
if you have
millions of hits every day.

00:07:54.801 --> 00:07:56.634
And these are the things
that help you

00:07:56.634 --> 00:07:59.167
to grow your business
really fast.

