One great example
is FooPets,

00:18:43.801 --> 00:18:47.534
where they actually
integrated a dog food brand

00:18:47.534 --> 00:18:49.100
very nicely into the game

00:18:49.100 --> 00:18:53.000
so the users don't feel like
they're really being hard sold.

00:18:53.000 --> 00:18:54.167
So here's an example--

00:18:54.167 --> 00:18:59.968
an application
that is featuring Coca Cola.

00:18:59.968 --> 00:19:02.767
Coke sponsored
this application.

00:19:02.767 --> 00:19:05.834
The application includes
ways to share and send

00:19:05.834 --> 00:19:09.200
