00:19:09.200 --> 00:19:10.567
there's an area for users

00:19:10.567 --> 00:19:14.133
to submit input
and write their own stories.

00:19:14.133 --> 00:19:16.667
Here's the FooPets example,

00:19:16.667 --> 00:19:19.367
where, you know,
you can buy your pet some food.

