and brands together.

00:19:35.968 --> 00:19:41.667
So those are kind of the three
probably most popular one--

00:19:41.667 --> 00:19:43.100
methods of making money.

00:19:43.100 --> 00:19:46.601
There's a few other techniques
that are out there.

00:19:46.601 --> 00:19:48.000
One is to create an app

00:19:48.000 --> 00:19:50.634
where it's free to use
in the beginning.

00:19:50.634 --> 00:19:52.667
