they're gonna
charge you for that,

00:20:00.934 --> 00:20:03.534
so it's a premium
model here.

00:20:03.534 --> 00:20:07.834
There's also donation
type of revenue models,

00:20:07.834 --> 00:20:12.601
where essentially people
are donating money to a cause.

00:20:12.601 --> 00:20:14.534
A cause is a very
popular example.

00:20:14.534 --> 00:20:17.968
You can also make money
by building custom applications

00:20:17.968 --> 00:20:19.934
for other companies.

00:20:19.934 --> 00:20:21.834
And then the last
way here--

00:20:21.834 --> 00:20:24.601
