in the early phases of this,

00:20:24.601 --> 00:20:27.834
but we are seeing
some third party applications

00:20:27.834 --> 00:20:31.200
developing special relationships
with social networks

00:20:31.200 --> 00:20:33.667
and then getting
featured placement,

00:20:33.667 --> 00:20:36.601
and in return
they're doing revenue share

00:20:36.601 --> 00:20:38.834
with those companies.

00:20:38.834 --> 00:20:41.367
It's kind of a long shot
probably for most companies,

00:20:41.367 --> 00:20:43.634
but it does exist
out there

00:20:43.634 --> 00:20:44.968
for companies
that have something

00:20:44.968 --> 00:20:47.267
really compelling
for a social network.

